 lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d9/1701/8d/6dec65e8c95b96b5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d4/1701/69/4137bc71a4636b5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d2/1701/94/905f3f010030fdb5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d0/1701/f0/48ba8026113f50b5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d4/1701/91/79a90b7bcbd8fdb5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d2/1701/83/1c85e37356b0e5b5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d1/1701/80/e9fed0c8eb9852b5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d4/1701/50/f23c8d21a0b6f1b5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d7/1701/3e/4fe50f80e19acab5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d9/1701/d9/b565ed8f559007b5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d4/1701/dc/327173311a9e09b5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d3/1701/56/0f5ba5a3907fceb5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d6/1701/65/05854eaa1a0db5b5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d2/1701/93/3344235166520db5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d7/1701/7f/40dc222199806cb5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d1/1701/bc/5c0a5a40c4ca08b5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <span class=\"tri\"></span>\r\n	<div class=\"img_txt\">\r\n		<p>\r\n			以上的单人表演的变脸是不是非常的精彩呢？那么接下来还有更为精彩的变脸术。\r\n		</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n<img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d0/1701/34/0de80f2b08a591b5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d8/1701/1e/324f8ca072ef17b5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d7/1701/24/f209ec285f2e55b5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d4/1701/1a/55a5f668b70451b5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d3/1701/d6/2d55ecb17cfdb5b5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d1/1701/6b/ba96a7563bbf29b5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d9/1701/fb/813cf63635a7fbb5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d6/1701/d3/e5f5d60e522ddab5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <span class=\"tri\"></span>\r\n	<div class=\"img_txt\">\r\n		<p>\r\n			以上的变脸不仅仅是自己本人真实的脸在变化，还有就是其他身上的假脸也会跟着一起变化，这是不是非常的神奇呀？这样的神奇才是变脸值得令人新奇的地方了。这就是在国粹之中最大的亮点了。\r\n		</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n<img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d3/1701/31/338873660c49b8b5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d1/1701/e8/e36cfa93f430f5b5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d6/1701/5d/fdd0d4dd22328ab5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d0/1701/c8/8f302623ea0547b5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <span class=\"tri\"></span>\r\n	<div class=\"img_txt\">\r\n		<p>\r\n			所有的表演变脸的大师们都是卸妆与大家一起认识下了，我们都为大师们精彩的表演艺术与精湛的水平而佩服不已。\r\n		</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n<img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d7/1701/e4/064cb97714dc4eb5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <span class=\"tri\"></span>\r\n	<div class=\"img_txt\">\r\n		<p>\r\n			年轻而貌美的主持人也出来与众多演员一起出来了，估计这精彩的表演是很快要结束了吧？美好的时间过的都是如此的快速！\r\n		</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n<img class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg lazyload\" src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d6/1701/32/870a95ea12c22eb5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"431\" /> <span class=\"tri\"></span>\r\n	<div class=\"img_txt\">\r\n		<p>\r\n			缘聚缘散，天下无不散之筵席嘛。喜欢这样的演出的下次可以多多来看几回。面对如此专业而精彩的川剧演员队伍，怎么能不喜欢呢？\r\n		</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>', '17', '锦江剧场(芙蓉国粹变脸秀)');
INSERT INTO `youjidiv` VALUES ('258', '酒店住宿', '<div class=\"b_poi_info b_poi_item\" id=\"ele-2343856-2\">\r\n	<div class=\"bottom\">\r\n		<div class=\"e_img_schedule\">\r\n			<div class=\"imglst\">\r\n				<div class=\"text js_memo_node\">\r\n					<p class=\"first\">\r\n						恒大集团作为大手笔入驻酒店业，确实在硬件方面的投入要比一般五星级酒店要奢侈很多。第一次入住了武汉恒大酒店之后，于是对恒大酒店这样的硬件设施与配套服务可谓是恋恋不忘了，因此每次去一个城市的时候第一时间选择的不是香格里拉、也不是洲际酒店，而是恒大集团的恒大酒店。之所以选择很大就是因为拥有着很高的性价比，价位与国际连锁的五星级酒店价格差不多。硬件设施要更多，每个设施都是独立的建筑大楼，规格与规模都是相当雄厚的。这一次来<a href=\"http://travel.qunar.com/p-cs300085-chengdu\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link_dest\">成都</a>游玩发现<a href=\"http://travel.qunar.com/p-cs300085-chengdu\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link_dest\">成都</a>有两家恒大酒店。于是山野君我义无反顾的选择了这两家恒大酒店了，那么现在就分享一下我来<a href=\"http://travel.qunar.com/p-cs300085-chengdu\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link_dest\">成都</a>入住的第一家恒大酒店的金堂恒大酒店。\r\n					</p>\r\n				</div>\r\n<img title=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" alt=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg\" src=\"https://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d8/1701/f5/6e1e8aadcca679b5.jpg_r_680x450x95_5cabdc30.jpg\" width=\"680px\" height=\"450px\" /><span class=\"tri\"></span>\r\n				<div class=\"img_txt\">\r\n					<p>\r\n						酒店在外观上是一如既往的给人是高端大气上档次的第一印象。与武汉恒大酒店不同的是，<a href=\"http://travel.qunar.com/p-oi5762583-chengdujintanghengdajiu\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link_dest\">成都金堂恒大酒店</a>的客房中心的门口就是一座景色如诗如画般的湖水。众所周知的是水是能够调节人居环境的干湿度平衡的，从入住的舒适度的角度而言是非常受人欢迎的。从外观整体上的视觉效果也算更加令人称赞的。整个酒店客房住宿的楼层为8层高，高度属于五星级酒店的标准规范。\r\n					</p>\r\n				</div>\r\n<img title=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" alt=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg\" src=\"https://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d2/1701/e8/a3b6a1d28ad07ab5.jpg_r_680x450x95_ab7db244.jpg\" width=\"680px\" height=\"450px\" /><span class=\"tri\"></span>\r\n				<div class=\"img_txt\">\r\n					<p>\r\n						从金堂恒大世博中心进入之后步行大约5分钟左右就能够看得到这座以客房为中心的主体大楼，看起来与其他恒大酒店的风格完全一样，一样的舒服一样的感觉。这样感觉很赞的呢。\r\n					</p>\r\n				</div>\r\n<img title=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" alt=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg\" src=\"https://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d5/1701/f8/930f3be169a88eb5.jpg_r_680x450x95_b664011d.jpg\" width=\"680px\" height=\"450px\" /><span class=\"tri\"></span>\r\n				<div class=\"img_txt\">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<a href=\"http://travel.qunar.com/p-cs300085-chengdushi\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link_dest\">成都市</a>金堂恒大酒店的正大门口下面就是很醒目的<a href=\"http://travel.qunar.com/p-oi5762583-chengdujintanghengdajiu\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link_dest\">成都金堂恒大酒店</a>几个大字，标志性的大字立马让人觉得身在四川<a href=\"http://travel.qunar.com/p-cs300085-chengdu\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link_dest\">成都</a>金堂恒大了。\r\n					</p>\r\n				</div>\r\n<img title=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" alt=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg\" src=\"https://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d3/1701/ba/0f10a0802e55d0b5.jpg_r_680x450x95_10539a82.jpg\" width=\"680px\" height=\"450px\" /><span class=\"tri\"></span>\r\n				<div class=\"img_txt\">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<a href=\"http://travel.qunar.com/p-cs300085-chengdushi\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link_dest\">成都市</a>金堂恒大酒店大门的气势相当的不错，走在这里会给人一种超越一大半奢华五星级酒店的其实呢，有没有呢？\r\n					</p>\r\n				</div>\r\n<img title=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" alt=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg\" src=\"https://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d7/1701/b4/b72ac0f15a823eb5.jpg_r_680x450x95_a23cd740.jpg\" width=\"680px\" height=\"450px\" /><span class=\"tri\"></span>\r\n				<div class=\"img_txt\">\r\n					<p>\r\n						酒店外观大门口。\r\n					</p>\r\n				</div>\r\n<img title=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" alt=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg\" src=\"https://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d0/1701/6f/ae61093c4e7f97b5.jpg_r_680x450x95_4ad95bd9.jpg\" width=\"680px\" height=\"450px\" /><span class=\"tri\"></span>\r\n				<div class=\"img_txt\">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<a href=\"http://travel.qunar.com/p-cs300085-chengdushi\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link_dest\">成都市</a>金堂恒大酒店的大厅环境优雅，属于典型的现代化奢华酒店大厅的风格。气场方面也是非常的充分的呢。\r\n					</p>\r\n				</div>\r\n<img title=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" alt=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg\" src=\"https://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d3/1701/d3/03a9a716b2d246b5.jpg_r_680x450x95_3db9077c.jpg\" width=\"680px\" height=\"450px\" /><img title=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" alt=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg\" src=\"https://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d5/1701/db/f61be39f1ae05eb5.jpg_r_680x450x95_05ad0043.jpg\" width=\"680px\" height=\"450px\" /><img title=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" alt=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg\" src=\"https://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d8/1701/f0/0fef5debf715c8b5.jpg_r_680x450x95_f445b2fd.jpg\" width=\"680px\" height=\"450px\" /><span class=\"tri\"></span>\r\n				<div class=\"img_txt\">\r\n					<p>\r\n						酒店客房的走廊。\r\n					</p>\r\n				</div>\r\n<img title=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" alt=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg\" src=\"https://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d5/1701/85/cdb7fbc6f1a1bb5.jpg_r_680x450x95_c6934fe0.jpg\" width=\"680px\" height=\"450px\" /><span class=\"tri\"></span>\r\n				<div class=\"img_txt\">\r\n					<p>\r\n						我入住的房间。\r\n					</p>\r\n				</div>\r\n<img title=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" alt=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg\" src=\"https://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d9/1701/9b/f59880ec01884fb5.jpg_r_680x450x95_af34a862.jpg\" width=\"680px\" height=\"450px\" /><img title=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" alt=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg\" src=\"https://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d6/1701/4c/a35cb3b5c89e26b5.jpg_r_680x450x95_513a94ea.jpg\" width=\"680px\" height=\"450px\" /><img title=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" alt=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg\" src=\"https://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d4/1701/7c/f7a71005eaa353b5.jpg_r_680x450x95_7894bf33.jpg\" width=\"680px\" height=\"450px\" /><img title=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" alt=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg\" src=\"https://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d1/1701/36/975b0437e577f6b5.jpg_r_680x450x95_c33966f1.jpg\" width=\"680px\" height=\"450px\" /><img title=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" alt=\"成都金堂恒大酒店图片\" class=\"box_img js_box_img js_lazyimg\" src=\"https://img1.qunarzz.com/travel/d2/1701